com.fishsemi.sdk.aircontrol

Class AirController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fishsemi.sdk.aircontrol.AirController

  • public class AirController
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is responsible to interact with air board. It provide methods to take photo, start/stop video recording, setup Uart baudrate, switch video stream source ID, etc.
